<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="less-adv">less <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /les/    美 /les/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>更少 / 小地；较少 / 小地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tom is <strong>less</strong> clever <strong>than</strong> his brother. 
汤姆不如他兄弟聪明。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I used to earn <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (不到) a pound a week when I first started work.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. less than  </p></div>